{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775867373599,"sessionID":"ses_2860ed2feffeB7qcd2ac0NdJM2","part":{"id":"prt_d79f1a3d50018TdX8PtE89FtMS","messageID":"msg_d79f1992b001laM1tvcEZAhNOj","sessionID":"ses_2860ed2feffeB7qcd2ac0NdJM2","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_f4ef1cd6e32847e99aa90899","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-026: K8s/AgentCube Provider\n2: \n3: ## Summary\n4: \n5: 实现 CLI 的双 Provider 部署能力，支持将 Agent 部署到标准 Kubernetes (Deployment + Service) 或 AgentCube AgentRuntime CRD。\n6: \n7: ## Purpose\n8: \n9: ### Background\n10: \n11: CLI 需要支持多目标部署平台:\n12: 1. **标准 Kubernetes**: 使用原生 Deployment + Service 资源\n13: 2. **AgentCube Platform**: 使用 AgentRuntime CRD (自定义资源)\n14: \n15: 当前 `KubernetesProvider` 和 `AgentCubeProvider` 已实现基础功能,但与 `cli-toolkit/spec.md` 中的需求存在差距。\n16: \n17: ### Goal\n18: \n19: 1. 完善 AgentRuntime CRD 部署逻辑,符合规范要求\n20: 2. 增强 Provider 错误处理和状态检测\n21: 3. 确保 `publish` 和 `status` 命令正确路由到对应 Provider\n22: \n23: ### Value\n24: \n25: - **多平台支持**: 同一 CLI 支持 K8s 和 AgentCube 两种部署目标\n26: - **一致性**: 统一的 Provider 接口抽象\n27: - **可观测性**: 完整的状态查询能力\n28: \n29: ---\n30: \n31: ## Scope\n32: \n33: ### In-Scope\n34: \n35: | Component | Path | Description |\n36: |-----------|------|-------------|\n37: | AgentCubeProvider | `agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py` | AgentRuntime CRD 部署 |\n38: | KubernetesProvider | `agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py` | K8s Deployment/Service |\n39: | PublishRuntime | `agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py` | publish 命令编排 |\n40: | StatusRuntime | `agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py` | status 命令编排 |\n41: | Unit tests | `tests/test_k8s_provider.py` 等 | 测试覆盖 |\n42: \n43: ### Out-of-Scope\n44: \n45: - CLI 参数变更 (已有 `--provider` 支持)\n46: - Python SDK 修改\n47: - client-go 代码生成\n48: \n49: ---\n50: \n51: ## Impact Analysis\n52: \n53: ### Dependencies\n54: \n55: | Dependency | Purpose | Status |\n56: |------------|---------|--------|\n57: | `kubernetes>=28.0.0` | K8s API 调用 | Optional dep |\n58: | `pydantic>=2.0.0` | 数据验证 | Existing |\n59: | `pyyaml>=6.0` | YAML 序列化 | Existing |\n60: \n61: ### Upstream\n62: \n63: - `cli-toolkit/design.md` — Provider 设计\n64: - `cli-toolkit/spec.md` — 部署需求\n65: \n66: ### Downstream Consumers\n67: \n68: 1. **CLI 用户** — 通过 `kubectl-agentcube publish --provider=agentcube|k8s`\n69: 2. **CI/CD 流水线** — 自动化部署\n70: \n71: ### Risks\n72: \n73: | Risk | Severity | Mitigation |\n74: |------|----------|------------|\n75: | K8s 库未安装 | Low | 优雅降级到 mock 模式 |\n76: | CRD 未安装 | Medium | 错误提示明确 |\n77: | 网络超时 | Medium | 配置超时参数 |\n78: \n79: ---\n80: \n81: ## Alternatives Considered\n82: \n83: ### Option 1: 仅支持 K8s Deployment (Not Selected)\n84: \n85: 不实现 AgentRuntime CRD 支持,仅使用原生 K8s 资源。\n86: \n87: **Cons**:\n88: - 不符合 AgentCube 平台需求\n89: - 无法使用 AgentCube 特有功能 (session 管理)\n90: \n91: ### Option 2: 仅支持 AgentCube CRD (Not Selected)\n92: \n93: 仅通过 AgentRuntime CRD 部署。\n94: \n95: **Cons**:\n96: - 需要 AgentCube CRD 预先安装\n97: - 灵活性不足\n98: \n99: ### Option 3: 双 Provider 支持 (Selected)\n100: \n101: 同时支持 KubernetesProvider 和 AgentCubeProvider,通过 `--provider` 参数选择。\n102: \n103: **Pros**:\n104: - 灵活性高\n105: - 兼容多种部署场景\n106: - 符合设计规范\n107: \n108: ---\n109: \n110: ## Implementation Plan\n111: \n112: ### Phase 1: AgentCubeProvider 增强\n113: \n114: - [ ] 添加 `imagePullSecrets` 支持 (默认 `default-secret`)\n115: - [ ] 确保 `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` / `ROUTER_URL` 在 env_vars 中\n116: - [ ] 添加 `delete_agent_runtime` 方法\n117: \n118: ### Phase 2: Status 增强\n119: \n120: - [ ] 完善 `_get_cr_k8s_status` 状态解析\n121: - [ ] 处理 CR 存在但无 status 的情况\n122: - [ ] 添加单元测试覆盖\n123: \n124: ### Phase 3: 错误处理\n125: \n126: - [ ] 统一 Provider 异常类型\n127: - [ ] 添加超时配置支持\n128: - [ ] 完善日志输出\n129: \n130: ### Phase 4: 测试\n131: \n132: - [ ] 补充 AgentCubeProvider 单元测试\n133: - [ ] 集成测试 publish/status 流程\n134: \n135: ---\n136: \n137: ## Acceptance Criteria\n138: \n139: ### AgentCubeProvider\n140: \n141: | ID | Scenario | Expected Result |\n142: |----|----------|-----------------|\n143: | AC-001 | deploy_agent_runtime | 创建 AgentRuntime CR |\n144: | AC-002 | imagePullSecrets | 默认包含 `default-secret` |\n145: | AC-003 | get_agent_runtime | 正确获取 CR 状态 |\n146: | AC-004 | 环境变量注入 | WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL 自动注入 |\n147: \n148: ### KubernetesProvider\n149: \n150: | ID | Scenario | Expected Result |\n151: |----|----------|-----------------|\n152: | K8S-001 | deploy_agent | 创建 Deployment + Service |\n153: | K8S-002 | node_port | 正确设置 NodePort 范围 |\n154: | K8S-003 | wait_for_deployment_ready | 超时抛出 TimeoutError |\n155: | K8S-004 | delete_agent | 清理 Deployment 和 Service |\n156: \n157: ### Publish Command\n158: \n159: | ID | Scenario | Expected Result |\n160: |----|----------|-----------------|\n161: | PUB-001 | provider=agentcube | 调用 AgentCubeProvider |\n162: | PUB-002 | provider=k8s | 调用 KubernetesProvider |\n163: | PUB-003 | 缺少 router_url | 抛出 ValueError |\n164: \n165: ### Status Command\n166: \n167: | ID | Scenario | Expected Result |\n168: |----|----------|-----------------|\n169: | STA-001 | agentcube provider | 返回 CR 状态 |\n170: | STA-002 | k8s provider | 返回 Deployment 状态 |\n171: | STA-003 | not_published | 返回提示信息 |\n172: \n173: ---\n174: \n175: ## Technical Design\n176: \n177: ### AgentCubeProvider 增强\n178: \n179: ```python\n180: # agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py\n181: class AgentCubeProvider:\n182:     def deploy_agent_runtime(\n183:         self,\n184:         agent_name: str,\n185:         image_url: str,\n186:         port: int,\n187:         entrypoint: Optional[str] = None,\n188:         env_vars: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None,\n189:         workload_manager_url: Optional[str] = None,\n190:         router_url: Optional[str] = None,\n191:         readiness_probe_path: Optional[str] = None,\n192:         readiness_probe_port: Optional[int] = None,\n193:     ) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n194:         # 1. 准备环境变量\n195:         final_env_vars = env_vars or {}\n196:         if workload_manager_url and \"WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL\" not in final_env_vars:\n197:             final_env_vars[\"WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL\"] = workload_manager_url\n198:         if router_url and \"ROUTER_URL\" not in final_env_vars:\n199:             final_env_vars[\"ROUTER_URL\"] = router_url\n200:         \n201:         # 2. 构建 AgentRuntime spec\n202:         agent_runtime = {\n203:             \"apiVersion\": f\"{self.CR_GROUP}/{self.CR_VERSION}\",\n204:             \"kind\": \"AgentRuntime\",\n205:             \"metadata\": {\n206:                 \"name\": agent_name,\n207:                 \"namespace\": self.namespace,\n208:             },\n209:             \"spec\": {\n210:                 \"maxSessionDuration\": \"8h\",\n211:                 \"sessionTimeout\": \"15m\",\n212:                 \"imagePullSecrets\": [{\"name\": \"default-secret\"}],\n213:                 # ... 其他字段\n214:             },\n215:         }\n216: ```\n217: \n218: ### Status 状态解析\n219: \n220: ```python\n221: # agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py\n222: def _get_cr_k8s_status(self, metadata: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n223:     # 处理多种状态:\n224:     # - status.phase 存在 -> 返回 phase\n225:     # - CR 存在但无 status -> \"created_no_status\"\n226:     # - CR 不存在 -> \"not_found\"\n227: ```\n228: \n229: ---\n230: \n231: ## Timeline Estimate\n232: \n233: | Phase | Effort |\n234: |-------|--------|\n235: | AgentCubeProvider 增强 | 2 hours |\n236: | Status 增强 | 1 hour |\n237: | 错误处理 | 1 hour |\n238: | 测试 | 2 hours |\n239: | **Total** | **6 hours** |\n240: \n241: ---\n242: \n243: ## Existing Implementation Status\n244: \n245: 当前实现位于:\n246: - `agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py` (296 行) — K8s 部署\n247: - `agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py` (218 行) — AgentRuntime 部署\n248: - `agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py` (321 行) — 发布编排\n249: - `agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py` (151 行) — 状态查询\n250: \n251: ### Current Gaps\n252: \n253: 1. **AgentCubeProvider**: 缺少 `imagePullSecrets` 配置\n254: 2. **AgentCubeProvider**: 环境变量注入逻辑不完整\n255: 3. **AgentCubeProvider**: 缺少 `delete_agent_runtime` 方法\n256: 4. **StatusRuntime**: CR 状态解析需完善\n257: 5. **测试覆盖**: AgentCubeProvider 单元测试不足\n\n(End of file - total 257 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-026: K8s/AgentCube Provider\n\n## Summary\n\n实现 CLI 的双 Provider 部署能力，支持将 Agent 部署到标准 Kubernetes (Deployment + Service) 或 AgentCube AgentRuntime CRD。\n\n## Purpose\n\n### Background\n\nCLI 需要支持多目标部署平台:\n1. **标准 Kubernetes**: 使用原生 Deployment + Service 资源\n2. **AgentCube Platform**: 使用 AgentRuntime CRD (自定义资源)\n\n当前 `KubernetesProvider` 和 `AgentCubeProvider` 已实现基础功能,但与 `cli-toolkit/spec.md` 中的需求存在差距。\n\n### Goal\n\n1. 完善 AgentRuntime CRD 部署逻辑,符合规范要求\n2. 增强 Provider 错误处理和状态检测","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775867373575,"end":1775867373596}}}}
{"type":"step_finish","timestamp":1775867373626,"sessionID":"ses_2860ed2feffeB7qcd2ac0NdJM2","part":{"id":"prt_d79f1a81f001AAL9dyMBn1NmQ1","reason":"tool-calls","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","messageID":"msg_d79f1992b001laM1tvcEZAhNOj","sessionID":"ses_2860ed2feffeB7qcd2ac0NdJM2","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":25654,"input":3827,"output":78,"reasoning":0,"cache":{"write":0,"read":21749}},"cost":0}}
{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775867377014,"sessionID":"ses_2860ed2feffeB7qcd2ac0NdJM2","part":{"id":"prt_d79f1b572001Ts9JiLyc9kNgiu","messageID":"msg_d79f1a85400115eyDhZKqFqcUm","sessionID":"ses_2860ed2feffeB7qcd2ac0NdJM2","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775867405907,"sessionID":"ses_2860ed2feffeB7qcd2ac0NdJM2","part":{"id":"prt_d79f1b8f7001mRPUvR481rJxR1","messageID":"msg_d79f1a85400115eyDhZKqFqcUm","sessionID":"ses_2860ed2feffeB7qcd2ac0NdJM2","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_de9ee8588ab74d19867ae88c","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-027: SDK CodeInterpreterClient\n\n## Summary\n\nImplement AgentCube Python SDK (`agentcube-sdk`) providing `CodeInterpreterClient` and `AgentRuntimeClient` for creating code interpreter sessions via the Workload Manager (control plane) and executing code/files via the Router (data plane).\n\n## Purpose\n\n### Background\n\nAgentCube infrastructure consists of:\n- **Control Plane (Workload Manager)**: Session lifecycle management\n- **Data Plane (Router)**: Code execution and file operations\n\nUsers need a Python client library to programmatically:\n1. Create/manage Code Interpreter sessions\n2. Execute commands and code remotely\n3. Perform file operations (read/write/upload/download)\n4. Invoke AgentRuntime workloads\n\n### Goal\n\nProvide a well-designed Python SDK that:\n- Abstracts HTTP communication details\n- Handles session lifecycle automatically\n- Follows Python best practices (context managers, proper exceptions)\n- Supports both Code Interpreter and Agent Runtime use cases\n\n### Value\n\n- **Developer Experience**: Simple `pip install agentcube-sdk` to get started\n- **Productivity**: High-level API vs raw HTTP calls\n- **Reliability**: Built-in retry, timeout, and error handling\n\n---\n\n## Scope\n\n### In-Scope\n\n| Component | Path | Description |\n|-----------|------|-------------|\n| Public API | `agentcube/__init__.py` | `CodeInterpreterClient`, `AgentRuntimeClient` exports |\n| CodeInterpreterClient | `agentcube/code_interpreter.py` | Session lifecycle, command execution, file ops |\n| AgentRuntimeClient | `agentcube/agent_runtime.py` | Session bootstrap, payload invocation |\n| ControlPlaneClient | `agentcube/clients/control_plane.py` | Session create/delete via Workload Manager |\n| CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient | `agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py` | Execute, files via Router |\n| AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient | `agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py` | Invoke via Router |\n| Utilities | `agentcube/utils/*.py` | HTTP session, token reading, logging |\n| Exceptions | `agentcube/exceptions.py` | `AgentCubeError`, `CommandExecutionError`, etc. |\n| Tests | `tests/*.py` | Unit and integration tests |\n\n### Out-of-Scope\n\n- Non-Python SDKs (Go, TypeScript, etc.)\n- Configuration dataclass (settings distributed across components)\n- Authentication beyond bearer token / service account file\n- Async support (future enhancement)\n\n---\n\n## Impact Analysis\n\n### Dependencies\n\n| Dependency | Purpose | Status |\n|------------|---------|--------|\n| `requests` | HTTP client | Required |\n| `PyJWT>=2.0.0` | JWT handling | Required |\n| `cryptography` | Crypto operations | Required |\n\n### Upstream\n\n- `python-sdk/design.md` — Current design\n- `python-sdk/spec.md` — Specification requirements\n\n### Downstream Consumers\n\n1. **Python developers** — Using `agentcube-sdk` in their applications\n2. **Internal services** — Agent execution workflows\n3. **CLI toolkit** — Potential integration with CLI\n\n### Risks\n\n| Risk | Severity | Mitigation |\n|------|----------|------------|\n| Router/Workload Manager unavailable | Medium | Clear error messages, timeout handling |\n| Session expiration | Medium | Proper TTL handling, reconnection logic |\n| Network timeouts | Low | Configurable timeouts, retry logic |\n\n---\n\n## Alternatives Considered\n\n### Option 1: Use existing `openai` Python library (Not Selected)\n\n**Pros**: Familiar API\n**Cons**: Does not support AgentCube's custom session/header protocol\n\n### Option 2: Generate SDK from OpenAPI spec (Not Selected)\n\n**Pros**: Automatic spec sync\n**Cons**: Spec not available; hand-crafted preferred for clarity\n\n### Option 3: Single `Configuration` class (Not Selected)\n\n**Pros**: Centralized configuration\n**Cons**: Distributed defaults match existing deployment patterns better\n\n### Option 4: Hand-crafted SDK (Selected)\n\n**Pros**: Full control over API design, clear documentation, follows spec exactly\n**Cons**: More implementation work\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Plan\n\n### Phase 1: Core Infrastructure\n\n- [ ] Set up `pyproject.toml` with dependencies\n- [ ] Create package structure (`agentcube/`)\n- [ ] Implement exception hierarchy\n- [ ] Implement utilities (HTTP session, token reader, logger)\n\n### Phase 2: Control Plane\n\n- [ ] Implement `ControlPlaneClient`\n- [ ] `create_session()` — POST to `/v1/code-interpreter`\n- [ ] `delete_session()` — DELETE with 404-as-success\n\n### Phase 3: Data Plane — Code Interpreter\n\n- [ ] Implement `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient`\n- [ ] `execute_command()` — POST to `api/execute`\n- [ ] `run_code()` — Write .py file + execute\n- [ ] File operations: `write_file`, `upload_file`, `download_file`, `list_files`\n\n### Phase 4: High-Level Client\n\n- [ ] Implement `CodeInterpreterClient`\n- [ ] Context manager support (`__enter__`/`__exit__`)\n- [ ] Session lifecycle (create → init data plane → cleanup)\n\n### Phase 5: Agent Runtime\n\n- [ ] Implement `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient`\n- [ ] `bootstrap_session_id()` — GET header inspection\n- [ ] `invoke()` — POST JSON payload\n- [ ] Implement `AgentRuntimeClient`\n\n### Phase 6: Testing\n\n- [ ] Unit tests for each client\n- [ ] Integration tests with mocked services\n- [ ] Example scripts (`examples/`)\n\n---\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n### CodeInterpreterClient\n\n| ID | Scenario | Expected Result |\n|----|----------|-----------------|\n| CI-001 | Context manager exit | Session deleted, HTTP closed |\n| CI-002 | Missing router_url | ValueError raised |\n| CI-003 | Execute non-zero exit | CommandExecutionError raised |\n| CI-004 | Python code execution | Timestamped .py file created and executed |\n\n### AgentRuntimeClient\n\n| ID | Scenario | Expected Result |\n|----|----------|-----------------|\n| AR-001 | Context manager exit | HTTP session closed |\n| AR-002 | Missing session_id header | ValueError raised |\n| AR-003 | Invoke without session_id | ValueError raised |\n\n### ControlPlaneClient\n\n| ID | Scenario | Expected Result |\n|----|----------|-----------------|\n| CP-001 | Create session | Returns sessionId from response |\n| CP-002 | Delete 404 | Returns True |\n| CP-003 | Missing workload_manager_url | Uses WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL env var |\n\n### DataPlaneClient\n\n| ID | Scenario | Expected Result |\n|----|----------|-----------------|\n| DP-001 | Execute command | Returns stdout |\n| DP-001 | Upload file | Multipart POST with session header |\n\n---\n\n## Technical Design\n\n### Public Exports\n\n```python\n# agentcube/__init__.py\nfrom .code_interpreter import CodeInterpreterClient\nfrom .agent_runtime import AgentRuntimeClient\n\n__all__ = [\"CodeInterpreterClient\", \"AgentRuntimeClient\"]\n```\n\n### CodeInterpreterClient\n\n```python\nclass CodeInterpreterClient:\n    def __init__(\n        self,\n        name: str = \"my-interpreter\",\n        namespace: str = \"default\",\n        ttl: int = 3600,\n        workload_manager_url: Optional[str] = None,\n        router_url: Optional[str] = None,\n        auth_token: Optional[str] = None,\n        verbose: bool = False,\n        session_id: Optional[str] = None,\n    ): ...\n    \n    def execute_command(self, command: str, timeout: Optional[float] = None) -> str: ...\n    def run_code(self, language: str, code: str, timeout: Optional[float] = None) -> str: ...\n    def write_file(self, content: str, remote_path: str) -> None: ...\n    def upload_file(self, local_path: str, remote_path: str) -> None: ...\n    def download_file(self, remote_path: str, local_path: str) -> None: ...\n    def list_files(self, path: str = \".\"): ...\n    def stop(self) -> None: ...\n```\n\n### Session Header\n\nAll Router requests include:\n```\nx-agentcube-session-id: {session_id}\n```\n\n### Timeout Defaults\n\n- Read timeout: 120 seconds\n- Connect timeout: 5.0 seconds\n- Per-call override supported\n\n---\n\n## Timeline Estimate\n\n| Phase | Effort |\n|-------|--------|\n| Core Infrastructure | 1 hour |\n| Control Plane | 2 hours |\n| Data Plane (Code Interpreter) | 3 hours |\n| High-Level Client | 2 hours |\n| Agent Runtime | 2 hours |\n| Testing | 3 hours |\n| **Total** | **13 hours** |\n\n---\n\n## Existing Implementation Status\n\nReference source: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/sdk-python/`\n\n### Package Layout\n\n| Path | Role |\n|------|------|\n| `pyproject.toml` | Package `agentcube-sdk`, dependencies |\n| `agentcube/__init__.py` | Public exports |\n| `agentcube/code_interpreter.py` | `CodeInterpreterClient` |\n| `agentcube/agent_runtime.py` | `AgentRuntimeClient` |\n| `agentcube/exceptions.py` | Exception classes |\n| `agentcube/clients/control_plane.py` | `ControlPlaneClient` |\n| `agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py` | `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` |\n| `agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py` | `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` |\n| `agentcube/utils/http.py` | `create_session` |\n| `agentcube/utils/utils.py` | `read_token_from_file` |\n| `agentcube/utils/log.py` | `get_logger` |\n\n### Current Gaps\n\n1. **No implementation exists** — Need to create from scratch\n2. **Testing infrastructure** — Need to set up test framework\n3. **Examples** — Need to provide usage examples","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/proposal.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/proposal.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/p